  <h2 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; position: relative; padding-bottom: 16px;">
    施術内容・使用製剤
    <span style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 60px; height: 2px; background: #726989;"></span>
  </h2>
  
